description:
This is a 21 minute workout called '20 Minute Mindfulness Meditation for Being Present | Mindful Movement' from the channel The Mindful Movement.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This is a guided meditation to help you develop your skill of being mindful and present.  It will reduce your stress level,  as well as improve your overall health and well being when practiced regularly. 

Written and read by Sara Raymond
An updated version of this meditation is available here: https://youtu.be/N6pji9kEO10
Music: 5 minute Meditative State Chris Collins, indiemusicbox.com
